  "text": "Furthermore, 10-to 17-year olds self-assessed their pubic hair status on the basis of Tanner-drawings [CITATION_1] . They were classified into three categories: pre-pubertal (Tanner stage 1), pubertal (Tanner stage 2 or 3) and post-pubertal (Tanner stage 4 to 6).",
