    "70952075": {
      "title": "Growth at Adolescence",
      "abstract": "Tanner need offer no apologies for this excellent book, which so clearly describes the changes in bodily form and function which occur during adolescence. We are in his debt for a succinct review of the major aspects of the physiologic changes of adolescence, clear illustrative material, hints for needed research and a bibliography which will prove invaluable to anyone interested in this field. The phenomena of physical growth, its orderlines and its variability, are described in detail."
